		<content translate="true">Language in the Home</content>
	</text>
	<text id="nav_text" x="223" y="425" width="555" height="" autosize="H" style="PROMPT" visible="false" fx="PROMPT_SHOW" hidefx="PROMPT_HIDE">
		<content translate="true">Click a &lt;B&gt;Lesson&lt;/B&gt; or &lt;B&gt;Activity&lt;/B&gt; to learn more about &lt;B&gt;Language in the Home.&lt;/B&gt;</content>
	</text>
	<section id="presentation_text" align="" spacing="0" autospace="false" columns="0" exclusive="false" expanded="true">
		<text id="text01" x="365" y="60" width="375" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">Parents sometimes wonder how often to talk with their children. The answer is easy: as often as possible.</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text02" x="365" y="110" width="410" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">Word learning depends upon the:&lt;LI&gt;Amount of talking&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Type of talking&lt;/LI&gt;</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text03" x="365" y="175" width="410" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">Conversational Patterns in the Home</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text04" x="365" y="200" width="400" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">&lt;LI&gt;Professional: 2153 words per hour = 11+ million per year&lt;/LI&gt;</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text05" x="365" y="220" width="410" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">&lt;LI&gt;Working Class: 1251 words per hour = 6+ million per year&lt;/LI&gt;</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text06" x="365" y="240" width="410" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">&lt;LI&gt;High Risk: 616 words per hour = 3+ million per year&lt;/LI&gt;</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text07" x="365" y="275" width="375" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">The key is back-and-forth conversations, not simply talking at the child.</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text08" x="365" y="315" width="375" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;&lt;B&gt;Key Message:&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;The ability to use language to effectively communicate with others is a key component in a child’s early development, and is dependent on the number of interactions between parent and child.&lt;/P&gt;</content>
		</text>
	</section>
